      "content": "hey so i had a small cyst removed by a doctor a few days ago in sydney and the cut is looking a bit weird. it's kinda red and feels warm and there's some yellow stuff oozing out of it but not a lot. can i just put some antibiotic cream on it and a warm compress to stop it? i dont really wanna go back to the clinic unless i have to",
