      "content": "i mean it's really not that much liquid and it's not really hurting, just a bit tender. i'm sure it's just standard healing stuff. if i just do the warm compress and use some neosporin, wouldn't that just help clean it out and make it better faster? i'm just trying to avoid the whole hassle of an appointment if it's just a minor thing.",
